<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<title>CMS - Express</title>
	<!-- Latest compiled and minified CSS & JS -->
	<link href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootswatch/4.0.0/flatly/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"> 
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/styles.css" media="screen" title="no title"> 
	 <script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script> 
	<script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery.js"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Indie+Flower&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="//code.jquery.com/ui/1.12.1/themes/base/jquery-ui.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/resources/demos/style.css">
  <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-1.12.4.js"></script>
  <script src="https://code.jquery.com/ui/1.12.1/jquery-ui.js"></script>
  <script>
  $( function() {
    $( "#accordion" ).accordion();
  } );
  </script>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
            <div class="column-col-md-12">

                <div id="carouselExampleIndicators" class="carousel slide fluid" data-ride="carousel">
                    <ol class="carousel-indicators">
                        <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
                        <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="1"></li>
                        <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="2"></li>
                    </ol>
                    <div class="carousel-inner">
                        <div class="carousel-item active">
                            <img class="item d-block w-100" src="/assets/houses.jpg" alt="First slide">
                        </div>
                        <div class="carousel-item">
                            <img class="item d-block w-100" src="/assets/dog.jpg" alt="Second slide">
                        </div>
                        <div class="carousel-item">
                            <img class="item d-block w-100" src="/assets/neighborhood.jpg" alt="Third slide">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="prev">
                        <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                        <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
                    </a>
                    <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="next">
                        <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                        <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
   </div>
   <div id="welcomebar">
       <h1 id="welcome">Welcome to neighBOARD!</h1
   </div>
   <div id="accordion">
  <h3 class="accordianHead">Step One: Add Yourself!</h3>
  <div>
    <p>
    In the NAVBAR, click on "Neighbors" - add your name and information (how many pets, children, and cars as applicable). Then, hit "Create Neighbor" - and you're in!
    </p>
  </div>
  <h3 class="accordianHead">Step Two: Look at the Board!</h3>
  <div>
    <p>
    In the NAVBAR, click on "The Board" - you can see posts from your neighbors. Maybe then move on to...
    </p>
  </div>
  <h3 class="accordianHead">Step Three: Post!</h3>
  <div>
    <p>
   In the NAVBAR, click on "Post." Introduce yourself, register a complaint, buy and sell, plan a neighborhood BBQ - the choice is up to you! The date and time will be added automatically. If you need to edit your post (or if you posted something silly and want to delete it), go to the Board and you will see buttons to do so. The post categories are:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Discussion</li>
      <li>Complaint</li>
      <li>Buy/Sell</li>
      <li>Events</li>
    </ul>
    <p>You also have to pick your name from the list - no anonymous posts here.</p>
  </div>
  <h3 class="accordianHead">Step Four: Remember!</h3>
  <div>
    <p>
    Be respectful and have fun! Happy clicking!
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
 
</body>





<script src="/assets/js/cms.js" type="text/javascript"></script>

</html>